Build:
1. export ESMFMKFILE=$PATH_TO_ESMF_MK_FILE
For example:
export ESMFMKFILE=/home/feiliu/ESMF/esmf/DEFAULTINSTALLDIR/lib/libg/Linux.gfortran.64.openmpi.default/esmf.mk

2. gmake

Run:
1. Retrieve grid description files 
wget --no-check-certificate https://raw.githubusercontent.com/feiliuesmf/esmftest/master/xgrid/test1/ll1deg_grid.nc
wget --no-check-certificate https://raw.githubusercontent.com/feiliuesmf/esmftest/master/xgrid/test1/ll2.5deg_grid.nc
3. mpirun -np $np ./xgridEx1
